oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph of Riley Drake and wife Nell (York) Drake
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of Riley Drake with his wife Nell (York) Drake of Robertson County. He is in uniform with overseas cap and medals, while she wears a dress of large checks with solid collar and waist. There is a picket fence to their right and and bushes on the left.
